<p>Head practice. I&rsquo;ve been having a tough time with hair-do&rsquo;s and beards. I can get absolutely lost in them sometimes and never feel like the painting is finished. Much like real hair do&rsquo;s I suppose, you&rsquo;ve got to set a time limit on how long you can fiddle around with it and then just move on and get out the house.</p>
